Um, so I made something even more serious.

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:39.220
I made an app potato mascot, um, which is this

00:08:39.220 --> 00:08:40.000
little guy.

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:42.620
Uh, I designed him and put him all over the place

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:43.000
.

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:44.000
There's lots of stickers.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.670
I'm sure you've seen some out in the, you

