know, there's probably lots more out there if you want

00:08:47.820 --> 00:08:48.000
one.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:49.740
Um, uh, and this is just, this is,

00:08:49.850 --> 00:08:52.000
this is kind of what I feel like sometimes.

